divs: Sighting DetailsI just saw your show ufos over earth in bucks county pa - there was a ufo report on the local news by the oxford valley mall it would have been in the same direction as the sightings on the show toward the air base the people who reported it to the news are from morrisville pa . I think in news report they had a picture i cant remember the actual date but it was earlier than the sightings on the show and the ufos were a different shape it was on KYW channel 3 news at 11 oclock or wpvi channel 6 i watch both so i don't remember what channel i was watching that night.
